data.description: Highly desired location in Meadow View off of Feagin Mill Road! A spacious 2 story home with 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 baths that is convenient to dining, shopping and schools. New roof and New HVAC systems installed in 2022! Gas stove, gas fireplace in great room, primary bedroom on main level, gutters with gutter guards throughout exterior, screened in detached building and this home even has a huge deck overlooking the spacious, private backyard...Make your appointment today!
